	<summary>Provides a custom UWP ScrollViewer - check description for more details.</summary>
    <description>Designed as a replacement for Microsoft's sealed ScrollViewer that captures mouse events and doesn't allow multiple inputs to children (e.g. two or more InkCanvases). Supports all the basic functions of a scrollviewer : horizontal/vertical panning and zooming.</description>
    <releaseNotes>Added ViewChanged event, ChangeView method and ZoomMode property.</releaseNotes>
